snippet: An SUV surged forward from a parking space into a small crowd waiting outside a Los Angeles-area ice cream parlor, killing a 73-year-old woman and leaving six people injured....

headline.print_headline: SUV Rams People at Ice Cream Shop; 1 Dead, 6 Hurt
headline.main: SUV Rams People at Ice Cream Shop; 1 Dead, 6 Hurt

lead_paragraph: An SUV surged forward from a parking space into a small crowd waiting outside a Los Angeles-area ice cream parlor, killing a 73-year-old woman and leaving six people injured.
